snippet.title: Puke the Pirate: Rebarfed - Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY ONLINE: https://gd.games/vampyscastle/puke-the-pirate-rebarfed

The grossest pirate is back with a brand new remake of Puke the Pirate!
Revisit Spatter Island and collect as much of Black Barf's treasure as you can!

Made with GDevelop. Based on the original game "Puke the Pirate".
